#~ "skiftläge eller små och stora bokstäver för texten som för närvarande är "
#~ "markerad."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You may choose between several styles of capitalization, including all "
#~ "lower or uppercase, book style capitalization where each word except "
#~ "conjunctions has an initial capital letter, and sentence style "
#~ "capitalization where the first word in a sentence is capitalized. You can "
#~ "also toggle the case, so that uppercase becomes lowercase, and vice versa."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Du kan välja bland flera olika sorters skiftlägen, inklusive alla små "
